{"tid":677820,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實做人朋友真係好難","createTime":"2018-05-25T13:42:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-25T19:36:19.000Z","uid":71176,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4759d7ac92ff651f3ad0e5b28f3af3662d8e7d1d","tid":677820,"uid":71176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T13:42:16.000Z","msg":"我到今時今日都唔撚明<br />\n朋友到底係乜 又要點做人朋友<br />\n應唔應該以真心待人呢？<br />\n應唔應該講真話呢？<br />\n之前我朋友發脾氣話要自己一個出去住<br />\n我好心同佢講 搬出去住好辛苦 衣食住行租金全部自己俾<br />\n賺錢唔容易 何況佢得中五 工作選擇就更少<br />\n全職租樓都難 半工讀仲點生存<br />\n佢係獨生子 基本上要乜有乜 <br />\n例如佢想出國留學父母都俾佢<br />\n之前佢有翻工 不過翻左一日就話好辛苦無做<br />\n相較之下 佢要自力更生真係好難想象<br />\n結果我就俾佢屌 話我唔明佢 話我做多左<br />\n又話我將我嘅價值觀夾硬放喺佢度<br />\n又話做好人無用 你點對人唔代表人點對你<br />\n佢咁講我真係好撚傷心同失望<br />\n其實我只係唔想佢仆街所以先講個現實俾你聽啫<br />\n真心當人朋友會食花生睇住佢死咩<br />\n但係就俾佢屌返轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能你哋會話其實唔使理佢咁多<br />\n但係係我角度而言 如果嗰條友行緊去死你唔拉住佢又點叫做朋友呢..<br />\n到底朋友之道係點樣<br />\n有冇巴絲打可以教下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68bbcccdf65902cba167160dabcea5e7c557c424","tid":677820,"uid":104038,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T13:59:35.000Z","msg":"你朋友唔成熟啫 忠言逆耳 你已經盡左作為朋友既責怪提醒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22e51e6a6973955a08f3bd661f0b2fedf8873082","tid":677820,"uid":71176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68bbcccdf65902cba167160dabcea5e7c557c424","tid":677820,"uid":104038,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T13:59:35.000Z","msg":"你朋友唔成熟啫 忠言逆耳 你已經盡左作為朋友既責怪提醒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T14:19:09.000Z","msg":"其實件事已經過左去<br />\n佢到今時今日都仲係咁諗 係到提<br />\n仲要係話翻我轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屈話係我硬頸"},{"pid":"97c47f4c8e37dcc786ba4dd95d1898d9f304246a","tid":677820,"uid":116942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T14:32:45.000Z","msg":"講左就算啦，有得做既都做左。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb85bee14a0a7d88c9f04747a2c95f181468fadc","tid":677820,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T15:44:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做人朋友</blockquote><br />\n語病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bca03203f80a4c712d2e8d03612610c5cae0d5b9","tid":677820,"uid":74962,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T16:26:18.000Z","msg":"咁有冇做多右 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e00e9fb3dcdb0b9ad867b5a82f7ab11d3be16e8e","tid":677820,"uid":106296,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T16:29:34.000Z","msg":"其實我都覺得有時有啲人我真係不得不放棄，價值觀差太多"},{"pid":"929c156985f1aa34ced3ff2199863bbbc653f2b7","tid":677820,"uid":71176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e00e9fb3dcdb0b9ad867b5a82f7ab11d3be16e8e","tid":677820,"uid":106296,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T16:29:34.000Z","msg":"其實我都覺得有時有啲人我真係不得不放棄，價值觀差太多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T17:48:26.000Z","msg":"中庸之道真係好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔想冇左呢個朋友但係又同佢相處唔到<br />\n同佢講野佢又唔啱聽"},{"pid":"d1b96d500dc457db40bf715c8db9c39ef1ec01da","tid":677820,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T18:18:01.000Z","msg":"佢一係火遮眼，一係on9，原諒佢一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e775df22415b146c7be993f406c8a06bb1bd65e4","tid":677820,"uid":71176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1b96d500dc457db40bf715c8db9c39ef1ec01da","tid":677820,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T18:18:01.000Z","msg":"佢一係火遮眼，一係on9，原諒佢一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T19:36:19.000Z","msg":"呢件事都成年前 但係去到今時今日仲講緊仲要係覺得係我錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢話我做多左 唔理解佢"}]}